net.sf.mpxj.common

Class MultiDateFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.text.Format
      • java.text.DateFormat
        • net.sf.mpxj.common.MultiDateFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MPXJDateFormat, MPXJTimeFormat

    public class MultiDateFormat
extends DateFormat
    This class wraps the functionality provided by the SimpleDateFormat class to make it suitable for use with the time conventions used in MPX files.
    See Also:
